      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not assessed at MRL 2; physical bench testing is not required for this computational surrogate assessment.",
      "rationale": "Physical test sample characterisation is not required at MRL 2 for this COU. The validation evidence is computational. Not assessed per MRL 2 scoping decision."
    },
