      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not assessed at MRL 2; equivalency between computational and physical inputs is addressed through the model inputs factor.",
      "rationale": "Formal equivalency assessment between computational input parameters and physical device parameters is not required at MRL 2. Input parameter correspondence is addressed under the Model Inputs factor. Not assessed per MRL 2 scoping decision."
